snippet.title: Demonlisher - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Originally released in 2004, this budget title was re-released on Steam in 2011 thanks to Strategy First (Who also owns the IP rights to Ghost Master and the Flatout series.)

What we have here is a maze chase game akin to Pac-Man, but with an ability to kill enemies using the left CRTL key. It is on Steam for 4.99 euro, but it usually goes on sale a lot for about 0.39c.

Demonlisher (C) Strategy First
Developed by Brain Bombers
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/321610/Demonlisher/
